Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of them? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How could there be three Rinnegans...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be his jutsu...\NThere's some trick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was busy preparing dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma, never mind that.\NJust focus on the opponent before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's about time\NI made my move!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on,\Nlet Sage Jutsu prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look above, upon the halos\Nand heavenly canopies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya the gallant--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Quit yakking in my ears!\N- Quit yakking in my ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My posturing keeps getting\N{\i1}interrupted today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this quickly and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get dinner ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma, that guy's eye is\Nmore important than dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay alert!\NIt's the ultimate ocular jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare belittle a housewife's dilemma\N of what to cook every day, you old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you use such a tone\Nagainst me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just looking after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are the ones yakking into\N{\i1}whose ears again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... Can we put your spousal\N differences aside and get this here over with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.10,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... Guess I'll just fry up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, you provide the oil.\NPa, you bring the Wind Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sage Art: Bath of Boiling Oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The oil vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They ought to have been blasted by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That one probably has tricks\Nup his sleeve too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we find out with close combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Massive Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...! He can absorb an entire jutsu?!\N So that's what he did earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We got his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He blocked my Sage Mode attack\N{\i1}without looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sage Art: Kebari Senbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not a single wasted movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would've gotten him if he'd dodged it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead he blocked it by summoning\N{\i1}without ever turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?\N {\i1}Blocking my attacks not just once, {\i1}but twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With no verbal signals or eye contact\N{\i1}between them at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if all three were sensory types,\N {\i1}they still have to see an attack {\i1}coming in order to counter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kebari Senbon is my fastest jutsu\N{\i1}with the widest attack range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only way to defend oneself\N {\i1}against it is with a shield, {\i1}as he just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And he did it without looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're no ordinary clones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You said they have a trick up\Ntheir sleeves, and you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:05:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we got their back earlier, you picked the\N target and attacked from his blind spot, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,During that time, one of the other guys\Nwas watching us the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were no signs that they were signaling\N each other either verbally or with eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's their eyes...\NAll three have the same eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Suppose the three of them can\Nshare what they see with each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Enabling their eyes to share images\Nwith one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what I suspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... What in tarnation are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Under these circumstances\N{\i1}where my ninjutsu are being nullified...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To face all three at once\N{\i1}is a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At this rate, if I enter battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be killed,\N{\i1}even in Sage Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never imagined\N{\i1}they would be this strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back for now, Jiraiya-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's escaped into the pipes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:57.74,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(748.125,576.25)}In Attendance,\N{\i1}The Six Paths of Pain\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We must analyze the Six Paths\Nand come up with a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll need some time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They may look different,\Nbut all possessed the same eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, they all have\Nthe Rinnegan of Six Paths...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if one of them is Nagato,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe there would be\Nso many Rinnegan users crawling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what in the world's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is the real Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Figuring out the main one\Nisn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,three of them possess\Nthe Rinnegan of Six Paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who...and what is Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know that yet.\NBut we can make a small deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their vision is linked,\Nand they share images.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ability those eyes hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means what, then?\NAnd how is it an advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Put simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way that three\Nsecurity cameras
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,show different angles of the same image,\N those three are able to see three views at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So if just one of them can see the target...\N the other two can counter with the ideal attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with perfect timing without having\Nto see their foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, their field of vision\Nis three times better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And unlike the Byakugan,\N they can always guard each other's blind spots
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,without weaving signs or\Nmanipulating chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder their combination\Nis invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to split them up\Nand fight each one separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm positive I can win one-on-one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they possess such eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,fighting as a team would have to\Nbe their basic mode of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taijutsu isn't going to work...\N and any ninjutsu will just be absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If taijutsu and ninjutsu won't work,\Nthen it'll have to be genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am a dud\Nwhen it comes to genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but as I recall you two were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... If they're former students\Nof yours, Jiraiya-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,they know that you don't use genjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that might give us an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm not gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,World peace is hanging\Non this battle, Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about no old geezer's\Nsenile prophecies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Lord Elder told us to\Nget along, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you\Nobject to so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sing a duet with Pa\Nat this plump ripe old age!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A duet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Our most powerful genjutsu involves appealing\N to the auditory senses of the victim through song.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Auditory senses? I see.\NThat's why we retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct...This genjutsu is powerful,\Nbut as soon as we make a sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,our whereabouts will be revealed,\Nwhich is its weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there's the harmony\Nof the sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the genjutsu\Nis placed with a melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires a little time\Nbefore it takes effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If they discover our whereabouts before they are\N caught in the genjutsu and attack, we will surely lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, once they are caught in the genjutsu,\N our victory will be assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If both your lives are ever in danger,\N I want you to free yourselves from my shoulders immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of the ninja world depends\Non this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan.\NAlthough it is a gamble as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...the croaking of frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a genjutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Shadow Clone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Giant Flame Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's your move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good! My gamble's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That big one went after\N{\i1} the jutsu to absorb it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first fellow only used summoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While both times, it was the big fellow\N{\i1}who absorbed my jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as I suspected, {\i1}each of them\N possesses {\i1}only a single type of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, the big fellow's eyes\N{\i1}are focused on the jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, I blinded earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So only one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is looking at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dark swamp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're really one-on-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You got us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You are inside a genjutsu paralysis\Nthat binds your psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now none of your bodies,\N including your main body, will be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect\Na genjutsu like this from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I taught you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Never let your guard down, no matter\Nwho your opponent is, Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You erred in your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to protect those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what kind of pain\N{\i1}I have to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than rule the world\Nthrough pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you had moved past the pain and harnessed\N your power to bring about peace in a positive way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That disciple will become a ninja {\i1}who will\N bring about {\i1} a great change to the ninja world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is what I saw in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Either great stability {\i1}or great destruction.\N {\i1}The likes of which this world {\i1}has never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For just a little while...\NI believed you were the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you both all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This genjutsu is hard on the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real hard keeping tempo with Pa...\NThis jutsu ain't that easy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Damages the throat!\NStretches the lower jaw 'til it sags! Creates wrinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My profound apologies.\NPlease take your rest now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For I've made my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you teach me to never\Nlet down your guard...Jiraiya Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lad! Your left arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's got a different face\Nthan the other three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He was probably summoned earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Before they got caught\Nin our genjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In attendance...\NThe Six Paths of Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Six?! There are six of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look close!\NThe three we just did in are there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The newly summoned ones must have\N resurrected them with some sort of jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's even a jutsu that can revive as many as\N three of them when they were undoubtedly dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.69,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pain... What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That name is an alias that\Ndenotes all six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,are there six Rinnegan bearers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...!
